data.description: Welcome home, this home is fresh and ready for you! Refinished living room hardwood floor looks great, plus you get an all new kitchen and bathroom too. Main floor has 1 bedroom and upstairs has two more.  Basement is unfinished and has open room for workshop, hobbies, workout, or storage area. Outside has steel siding for low maintenance.  Located in close proximity to all that St. Cloud has to offer, plus easy access to Highway 10 for a commute north or south.  Come check it out today!
